# Privacy Policy for Wordle Genie

Effective date: December 27th, 2023

This Privacy Policy describes how Wordle Genie (the "Extension") collects, uses, and discloses information, and what choices you have with respect to the information.

## Updates in this version of the Privacy Policy:

Reflects the functionalities of Wordle Genie.
Applicability of this Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy applies to the Extension's collection and use of your personal information (i.e., information that identifies a specific person, such as full name or email address).

## Information We Collect and Receive

Wordle Genie may collect and receive information about users in a few different ways:

**Data Collected Through User Interaction:** The Extension does not actively collect any personal information. Interaction with certain features may require access to the current webpage content when activated.
**Technical Information:** We may collect technical data about your browser type and version, but no personal or identifiable information is gathered.

## How We Use the Information

The information collected is used to:

Provide and maintain the functionality of the Extension.
Enhance user experience by optimizing the Extension's performance.
Sharing and Disclosure

Wordle Genie does not share or disclose any personal information. The Extension operates on a strict no-data-collection policy.

## Data Security

We are committed to protecting your information. Wordle Genie is designed with the utmost respect for your privacy and data security. No personal data is collected, stored, or transmitted.

## Changes to this Privacy Policy

Wordle Genie reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Please review it occasionally. If we make changes to this Privacy Policy, the updated version will be posted on this page.

